headline: Entegra to Integrate Moody’s Data, Advancing Data-Driven Insight in Structured-Credit Markets
summary: NEW YORK, November 24, 2025--Entegra LLC, an innovator in Trading as a Service (TaaS), today announced that it will integrate Moody’s Corporation’s (NYSE: MCO) cash flow analytics into its TaaS platform.
